// 21.305 — 🔒 PII console-leak arc-guard + 6 console.error fixes. NEW arc-guard `scripts/check-pii-console-leak.mjs` — catches `console.error("msg", err)` with raw Error object. Vercel function logs are NOT BAA-covered; Clerk/Twilio/Drizzle errors echo customer email/phone/order data into err.message. Fixed 6 violations across server components + client components: `app/order/confirmation/[id]/page.tsx` (server — `after()` callback) + `app/account/orders/page.tsx` (server) + `app/account/heroes/HeroesForm.tsx` + `app/account/profile/ProfileForm.tsx` + `components/MobileStickyCta.tsx` + `components/RecentlyViewedAutoStrip.tsx` — all changed raw `e` → `e instanceof Error ? e.name : String(e)`. Guard wired into `.githooks/pre-push` (12/12 gates). Sister scc v13.9005 + GW v2.97.AE + sureel + vrg v0.14.18 same-class port. Ported from CannAgent (v3.350/v4.235/v4.305/v4.525/v4.835).
// 21.205 — 🛡️ HTML entity arc-guard + 2 entity fixes. NEW arc-guard `scripts/check-html-entities-jsx.mjs` — scans 189 TS/TSX files for named HTML entities (`&middot;`, `&hellip;`, `&mdash;`, etc.) in JSX text that React does NOT decode (renders literally to user). Also catches numeric entities in `.ts` string literals. DEFERRED: curly-quote family (`&rsquo;`, `&ldquo;`, etc.) — fix is JSX-expression wrap, non-trivial across 30+ files. NEW arc-guard `scripts/check-server-actions-async.mjs` — catches non-async exports in "use server" files (Next 16 Turbopack deploy blocker). Both guards wired into `.githooks/pre-push` (11/11 gates). Entity fixes: `&middot;` → `·` in `app/order/confirmation/[id]/page.tsx:219` + `components/LoyaltyCard.tsx:90`. Sister scc v13.8905 + vrg v0.14.17 same-class port. Ported from GW v2.97.AD. Class history: v4.555/v4.575/v4.595/v4.615.
